::Dark Prime::

    He transformed to vechical mode and roared off towards =
the CF. (He should still register as Maximal, for now) As he neared it he t=
ransformed back to Robot Mode.
    "Hey, Maximals," He said into his comm. =
"It's Prime, will someone please come out here to.....talk."

::Eclipse::

=
    He sniffed for CyberShark's signal. On his way he picked up one that sm=
elled wrong, on it's way to the CF. He turned around and headed back.
    W=
alking in like he belonged, which he wasn't sure if he did or not, he looke=
d and saw a new robot standing near the CF. He smelled like Primal Prime, b=
ut that smell now was permiated with the stench of evil. 
    He turned aro=
und and went to the other side of the ship, hoping to find another entrance=
. (Is there one?)
